# Cloudflare Pages custom headers for docs.rulvar.com.
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
#
# Hashed build assets are immutable: the filename embeds a content
# hash, so a year-long client cache can never serve a stale byte.
# HTML keeps the platform default (max-age=0, must-revalidate), which
# is what makes instant post-deploy freshness work.
/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

# Pin the host to HTTPS for a year. The apex (rulvar.com) ships the
# same header from its own _headers file in the landing repository.
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
